      • getConnection

        public java.sql.Connection getConnection()
                                  throws java.sql.SQLException
        检索数据库本Transaction对象的数据库连接
        指定者:
        getConnection 在接口中 Transaction
        返回:
        DataBase connection
        抛出:

      • openConnection

        protected void openConnection()
                       throws java.sql.SQLException
        从dataSource中获取Connection, 然后给connection注入配置(level和autoCommit)
        抛出:
        java.sql.SQLException

      • setDesiredAutoCommit

        protected void setDesiredAutoCommit​(boolean desiredAutoCommit)
        参数:
        desiredAutoCommit - 如果和原来配置的一样, 就不会调用Connection.setAutoCommit(boolean)去改配置了
        抛出:
        TransactionException - 由于Connection.setAutoCommit(boolean)和Connection.getAutoCommit() 抛出的SQLException而产生的异常
